# Ignore Vivado / Xilinx generated files and build artifacts
# Keep source files, IP sources and project files but exclude generated runs, caches and reports

# Vivado journals, logs, reports, and binary outputs
*.jou
*.log
*.pb
*.rpt
*.vdi
*.dcp
*.vds
*.wdb
*.bit
*.bin

# Generated directories
**/runs/
**/*.runs/
**/sim/
**/sim_*/
**/hw/
**/soc.hw/
**/.cache/
**/xsim.dir/

# IP autogenerated simulation/netlist folders
**/ip_user_files/*/sim/
**/ip_user_files/*/sim_*/

# SDK/implementation files
**/sdk/
**/hw/

# Misc
*.backup.jou
*.jou.backup
*.jou~

# OS files
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# Temporary / editor files
*~
*.swp
*.swo